CoordinateSeries, LabeledNumberSeries, MixedSeries, NumberSeries, PointSeries
public abstract class AbstractSeries<DataType>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISeries<DataType>

Abstract implementation of ISeries, implementing all needed methods, except for ISeries.setData(Object). You should not need to implement this class by your own as the existing implementations should cover all possible variations supported by Highcharts.

Date: Feb 18, 2011 Time: 6:06:55 PM
